<HEADLINE>
<P>
ALTHOUGH IT'S LEGAL, ALCOHOL IS A DRUG 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
On Nov. 18, the headline ran: "Alcohol -- Not Drugs -- Detected in Tarpley." 
</P>
<P>
Please inform your headline writer, copy editor, the sports staff and the 
general public that alcohol is a drug. Period. 
</P>
<P>
Alcohol is a drug. Alcohol is a legal drug. Alcohol is the most used and abused 
drug in our nation. 
</P>
<P>
HUGH M. STEVENSON, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
