<P>
ELWAY, JOHN; NEWSPAPERS -- COLORADO; NEWS MEDIA; DENVER BRONCOS (FOOTBALL 
TEAM); FOOTBALL PLAYERS; RUMORS; PRIVACY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
