NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Children's Museum at La Habra opens its new 8,000-square-foot wing today at 
301 S. Euclid St., La Habra. Permanent displays on science, theater and 
preschool activities will be offered. Hours: 10 a.m. to 4 p.m. Admission: free. 
Information: (213) 905-9793. 
</P>
