-- MILITARY BASES -- PHILIPPINES; PHILIPPINES -- GOVERNMENT; MILITARY FORCE 
REDUCTIONS; AMERICANS -- PHILIPPINES; MALTA; SUMMIT CONFERENCES; AQUINO, 
