<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski was a $40 loser Friday when Ono Gummo ran 
third in the ninth race. The original wager was to be a win parlay from Bequest 
in the eighth to Ono Gummo but Bequest was scratched. The loss left him with a 
bankroll of $1,066.30. He started the meeting with a mythical bankroll of 
$1,000. 
</P>
<P>
For today, Bob's bet is a $30 win parlay from Phantom X. in the fourth to Firth 
of Tay in the sixth. 
</P>
<P>
Beginning Bankroll......$1,000 
</P>
<P>
Friday's Loss...........$40.00 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll........$1,066.30 
</P>
